Adding the item to the cart
- Create the route to add cart items.
- Check if there is a cart in the session.
- Save the cart item to the session.
 - Use the following structure:
  {                 total: 0,
  itemList: [
   {
   product: {
   _id: ObjectId{'#'},
   name: 'Some Product',
     description: 'This is an example',                
